            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> I like to configure it to tmpfs\n\nYou can do this already via `:help $NVIM_APPNAME` or `:help base-directories`.\n\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/a6f219b06bebf5878b970bebf53db7b942fe8731/runtime/lua/vim/lsp/log.lua#L35\n\nIn the case of log files (`stdpath('log')`), the xdg env var is `$XDG_STATE_HOME`.\n\n\nNot going to provide a specific option for LSP only.",
